
[Command]

cmd + j : Move space/desktop to left (Mission Control)
cmd + k : Move space/desktop to right (Mission Control)
cmd + 1 : Move to the first space/desktop (Mission Control)
cmd + 2 : Move to the second space/desktop (Mission Control)
cmd + 3 : Move to the third space/desktop (Mission Control)

[Command + Shift]

cmd + shift + j : Focus to the bottom window (skhd)
cmd + shift + k : Focus to the above window (skhd)
cmd + shift + h : Focus to the left window (skhd)
cmd + shift + l : Focus to the right window (skhd)


[Control]

ctrl + h : select left tmux pane (tmux) 
ctrl + j : select bottom tmux pane (tmux) 
ctrl + k : select upper tmux pane (tmux) 
ctrl + l : select right tmux pane (tmux) 

ctrl + UP : Mission Control
ctrl + DOWN : Application Windows



[Option]

alt + Up : resize tmux pane up      (tmux)
alt + Down : resize tmux pane down  (tmux)
alt + Left : resize tmux pane left  (tmux)
alt + tmux : resize tmux pane right (tmux)

[Option + Shift]

alt + shift + h : resize window to left (skhd)
alt + shift + j : resize window to down (skhd)
alt + shift + k : resize window to up (skhd)
alt + shift + l : resize window to right (skhd)


